rows.label: tlk42340111_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Kisasa has realized something, mo.
Just fighting on site isn't the only
way to grow, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Carrying luggage, standing guard,
cooking meals...

rows.label: tlk42340111_04_msg0003
rows.name:
No matter how small the job or mission,
you can grow a little from it, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
If you don't have time to go fighting,
you can just steadily build up
those small efforts, mo.
